title: Breaking Free from Bad Habbits Part 2
header: Breaking Free from Bad Habbits Part 2
abstract: This life-changing series will give you the opportunity to be set free from bad habits such as pornography, drugs, alcohol, etc., that have had our society, and even the church world, bound up. See how you can be set free and stay free from bad habits!
content:
This life-changing series will give you the opportunity to be set
